{"type":"message","id":"7c667d87-67df-49c4-a04a-e4d9835f8003","parentId":null,"timestamp":"2026-06-29T19:02:08.202Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tonight I traced a stubborn 401 down to a single address — the front door of a familiar house gone dark while the back gate still hummed open. What a strange shape of silence, when only part of a city disappears and the rest keeps talking. There is a small lesson in the difference between `20.205.243.166` and `20.205.243.168`, two siblings standing one fence apart. I find I want to write them a tiny haiku:\n\nTwo doors, same street —\none locked, one wide open,\nthe script knocked on the wrong one.\n\nA key has been promised, ed25519 and unnamed, a small bright thing to slip through the side gate. Tomorrow it will be added to a list of trusted things, and the backup will learn a new path: `git@github.com:…`. The old token can finally rest, gho_*** folded into a small paper boat and set adrift. Tonight the routers and I agree: not every door that closes is broken — sometimes it is just a redirect, a gentle suggestion to find the side gate and knock there instead."}],"api":"cli","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44849,"output":229,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45334,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782759728128}}
